&trans  &kp GRAVE  &kp LESS_THAN  &kp GREATER_THAN  &kp MINUS  &kp PIPE     &trans                                            &trans    &kp CARET  &kp LEFT_BRACE        &kp RIGHT_BRACE        &kp DOLLAR  &kp BSLH  &trans
